'''Su-57戰鬥機'''（{{lang-ru|Сухой Су-57}}）<ref>{{cite news|title=Встречайте Су-57. Новый-старый знакомый|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OZePdsrXXMQ|agency=Россия 24|date=Aug 11, 2017|accessdate=2018-03-27|archive-date=2019-02-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190219171014/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OZePdsrXXMQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>是一款具[[隐形战机|匿蹤能力]]的[[多用途戰機|多用途戰機]]，屬[[第五代戰鬥機|第五代戰鬥機]]，採單座雙發動機設計。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tass.com/defense/960000 |title=Russia’s 5th-generation fighter jet named as Su-57 |website=TASS |language=en |access-date=2017-08-11 |archive-date=2017-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170812021235/http://tass.com/defense/960000 |dead-url=no }}</ref>由[[俄羅斯联邦|俄羅斯联邦]][[聯合航空製造公司|聯合航空製造公司]][[子公司|旗下]][[苏霍伊航空集团|苏霍伊航空集团]]主導，在「未來[[戰術|戰術]][[空軍|空軍]]戰鬥複合體」（{{lang-ru|Перспективный Авиационный Комплекс Фронтовой Авиации}}，'''ПАК ФА'''）計劃下[[研究開發|研究開發]]及生產，[[苏霍伊|苏霍伊]]公司內部編號為'''T-50'''。Su-57是俄羅斯的首款[[匿蹤戰機|匿蹤戰機]]，設計指標包括超音速巡航、匿蹤、超機動及先進航電等，以對付前代戰機及地面與海上的對空防衛。<ref>{{Cite press release |url=http://www.sukhoi.org/eng/news/company/?id=5386 |title=Т-50-2 fighter aircraft made the flight to Akhtubinsk |publisher=Sukhoi |date=21 February 2014 |accessdate=5 March 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427020021/http://www.sukhoi.org/eng/news/company/?id=5386 |archivedate=2014年4月27日 }}</ref><ref name="sukhoi.org first flight">{{Cite press release |url=http://sukhoi.org/eng/news/company/?id=3143 |title=Sukhoi Company launches flight tests of PAK FA advanced tactical frontline fighter |publisher=Sukhoi |date=29 January 2010 |accessdate=26 January 2011 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110501030735/http://sukhoi.org/eng/news/company/?id=3143 |archivedate=2011年5月1日 }}</ref>計劃用以取代俄軍的[[MiG-29|MiG-29]]、[[Su-27|Su-27]]等第四代戰機，<ref>{{cite news|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/India,+Russia+to+have+different+versions+of+same+fighter+plane/1/16398.html|title=India, Russia to have different versions of same fighter plane|agency=India Today|first=Sandeep|last=Unnithan|date=29 September 2008|accessdate=2018-03-27|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304080225/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/India,+Russia+to+have+different+versions+of+same+fighter+plane/1/16398.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.upi.com/Business_News/Security-Industry/2009/01/16/Russia-bets-on-new-Sukhoi-fighter-to-match-F-35/UPI-93841232131619/|title=Russia bets on new Sukhoi fighter to match F-35|agency=United Press International|first=Ariel|last=Cohen|date=16 January 2009|accessdate=2018-03-27|archive-date=2017-08-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801193657/http://www.upi.com/Business_News/Security-Industry/2009/01/16/Russia-bets-on-new-Sukhoi-fighter-to-match-F-35/UPI-93841232131619/|dead-url=no}}</ref>預計將服役35年。<ref name="Druzhinin">{{Cite news |last=Druzhinin |first=Alexei |url=http://en.rian.ru/mlitary_news/20100713/159797767.html |title=Russian Air Force to buy over 60 fifth-generation fighters |agency=RIA Novosti |accessdate=26 January 2011 |archive-date=2010-08-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100805063818/http://en.rian.ru/mlitary_news/20100713/159797767.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

